#### invokevirtual
```
public int neg(int i) {
    return -i;
}

public int foo(int i) {
    return neg(neg(i));
}

// 对应的字节码
public int foo(int);
  descriptor: (I)I
  flags: ACC_PUBLIC
  Code:
    stack=3, locals=2, args_size=2
       0: aload_0
       1: aload_0
       2: iload_1
       3: invokevirtual     // Method neg:(I)I
       6: invokevirtual     // Method neg:(I)I
       9: ireturn
```

